	srcset=&#34;https://ddlgitgzzhm.github.io/p/system-summary-1/test2_hu_4af32515d225ab51.png 480w, https://ddlgitgzzhm.github.io/p/system-summary-1/test2_hu_74d19393d773e960.png 1024w&#34;
