        <item>
        <title>[交易心态] 兴尽悲来,识盈虚之有数</title>
        <link>https://ddlgitgzzhm.github.io/p/future-think-1/</link>
        <pubDate>Mon, 28 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://ddlgitgzzhm.github.io/p/future-think-1/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://ddlgitgzzhm.github.io/p/future-think-1/img.png" alt="Featured image of post [交易心态] 兴尽悲来,识盈虚之有数" /&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;兴尽悲来,识盈虚之有数&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;-《滕王阁序》&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;假若经历过 亲情、爱情、友情、物质的起落。&lt;/p&gt;
